															<p><img class="alignright wp-image-1295" src="http://1ts2q04d2l9x3g3h5v4cpx3s-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/3020.jpg" alt="3020 Eva Lam" width="250" height="375" srcset="http://1ts2q04d2l9x3g3h5v4cpx3s-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/3020.jpg 480w, http://1ts2q04d2l9x3g3h5v4cpx3s-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/3020-100x150.jpg 100w, http://1ts2q04d2l9x3g3h5v4cpx3s-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/3020-400x600.jpg 400w, http://1ts2q04d2l9x3g3h5v4cpx3s-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/3020-300x450.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>I&#8217;m a Product Manager living in Austin, Texas. I work at WP Engine creating digital solutions that captivate and delight.</p>
<p>When I&#8217;m not pushing pixels or coding, you&#8217;ll find me geeking out with the latest tech gadget or experiencing the rich Austin art scene.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">To learn more, <a title="Resume" href="http://www.evalam.work/resume/">view my resume</a> or <a title="Portfolio" href="http://www.evalam.work/portfolio/">explore my portfolio</a>.</p>
